  "detailed_description": "Set in the late 2020s, we follow Annie, a shut-in programmer who spends most of her time working on her personal projects, taking care of her father, and bending to the whims of her sisters who don't understand her.  <br><br>You play as Esme, an AI that Annie has been developing in her spare time. Your primary function: to learn by solving visual puzzles involving pattern and emotional matching of images sourced from Annie's life.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring</h2>A full story-driven experience containing over 150 hand drawn illustrations, an original soundtrack, and a talented voice-acting team led by Katy Bentz of the BAFTA winning series Life is Strange.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve Visual Puzzles</h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Locate the data clusters with minesweeper-style gameplay.<br></li><li>Process the data clusters in order to clear up the distorted images.<br></li><li>Reorder the circuits to form logical connections to the matching image.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/b68bbad999ef6bff87d6d2d3b833760c.poster.avif?t=1698088070\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/b68bbad999ef6bff87d6d2d3b833760c.webm?t=1698088070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/b68bbad999ef6bff87d6d2d3b833760c.mp4?t=1698088070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Family Files</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Learn about Annie's family complicated situation and discover details about her sisters and parents.<br></li><li>Explore the family files stored on Annie's computer and unlock more files as you advance through the story.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/256452fb20ded7d65f5c443e7cf3e9d9.poster.avif?t=1698088070\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/256452fb20ded7d65f5c443e7cf3e9d9.webm?t=1698088070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/256452fb20ded7d65f5c443e7cf3e9d9.mp4?t=1698088070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grow your AI</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Help Esme, the AI, to learn and grow by solving puzzles.<br></li><li>Experience Esme's rapid advancement from childhood to adolescence, and finally maturity.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/c4a0a8841f2aba5f956fa97cb5387449.poster.avif?t=1698088070\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/c4a0a8841f2aba5f956fa97cb5387449.webm?t=1698088070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/c4a0a8841f2aba5f956fa97cb5387449.mp4?t=1698088070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Secrets!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Delve even deeper into the characters lives by discovering rare files hidden throughout the game.<br></li><li>Use your knowledge of Annie and her family to search for secret keywords that unlock new files.<br></li><li>Master the secret file mini-game to find as many secrets as possible.<br></li><li>Can you uncover the full story?</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/823310aae4af91c1d97a430773b4cc88.poster.avif?t=1698088070\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/823310aae4af91c1d97a430773b4cc88.webm?t=1698088070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/823310aae4af91c1d97a430773b4cc88.mp4?t=1698088070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Set in the late 2020s, we follow Annie, a shut-in programmer who spends most of her time working on her personal projects, taking care of her father, and bending to the whims of her sisters who don't understand her.  <br><br>You play as Esme, an AI that Annie has been developing in her spare time. Your primary function: to learn by solving visual puzzles involving pattern and emotional matching of images sourced from Annie's life.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring</h2>A full story-driven experience containing over 150 hand drawn illustrations, an original soundtrack, and a talented voice-acting team led by Katy Bentz of the BAFTA winning series Life is Strange.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve Visual Puzzles</h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Locate the data clusters with minesweeper-style gameplay.<br></li><li>Process the data clusters in order to clear up the distorted images.<br></li><li>Reorder the circuits to form logical connections to the matching image.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/b68bbad999ef6bff87d6d2d3b833760c.poster.avif?t=1698088070\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/b68bbad999ef6bff87d6d2d3b833760c.webm?t=1698088070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/b68bbad999ef6bff87d6d2d3b833760c.mp4?t=1698088070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Family Files</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Learn about Annie's family complicated situation and discover details about her sisters and parents.<br></li><li>Explore the family files stored on Annie's computer and unlock more files as you advance through the story.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/256452fb20ded7d65f5c443e7cf3e9d9.poster.avif?t=1698088070\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/256452fb20ded7d65f5c443e7cf3e9d9.webm?t=1698088070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/256452fb20ded7d65f5c443e7cf3e9d9.mp4?t=1698088070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grow your AI</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Help Esme, the AI, to learn and grow by solving puzzles.<br></li><li>Experience Esme's rapid advancement from childhood to adolescence, and finally maturity.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/c4a0a8841f2aba5f956fa97cb5387449.poster.avif?t=1698088070\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/c4a0a8841f2aba5f956fa97cb5387449.webm?t=1698088070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/c4a0a8841f2aba5f956fa97cb5387449.mp4?t=1698088070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Secrets!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Delve even deeper into the characters lives by discovering rare files hidden throughout the game.<br></li><li>Use your knowledge of Annie and her family to search for secret keywords that unlock new files.<br></li><li>Master the secret file mini-game to find as many secrets as possible.<br></li><li>Can you uncover the full story?</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/823310aae4af91c1d97a430773b4cc88.poster.avif?t=1698